commitResults.messageBody:
Task.setStatus contradicts the immutability of Task and has already caused weird test failures.

Let's switch to Task.withCompletion, which returns a new Task with the change, similar to other immutable APIs. The tests have also been modified to modify the models used in their tests accordingly.
